      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall assign a prepared plane to either 'Operations' or 'Maintenance' based on its condition and schedule."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "If the plane still has scheduled flights, it continues being used in operations.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall keep a plane in the 'Operations' state if it still has scheduled flights."
    },
    {
      "source_requirement": "When no more flights are scheduled or maintenance is required, the system sends the plane for maintenance.",
      "rewritten_requirement": "The system shall send a plane to 'Maintenance' when there are no more scheduled flights or maintenance is required."
